        <h1>MAXIMILIANO HAAS</h1>
        <br/>

        <p style="text-align:justify;">Maximiliano is a DJ & Producer from Buenos Aires, Argentina. His career as a DJ started in 2007, soon enough he started performing in local nightclubs, events and private parties. To the date he has performed more than 800 gigs in some of the most important places in Argentina & around the world. He held a residency at +Clubone (Palacio Alsina), Pacha Buenos Aires, Jet BA, and Pueblo Limite. Besides, he has played in numerous occasions at Bahrein, The Shamrock Basement, Caix, Kika, Mod, and at his own parties. In 2016 he was on tour over the US and Uruguay, and in 2017 he was on tour in Europe playing in Spain, Serbia, & Austria with remarkable performances and great recognition by the crowd.
            <br/><br/>
            As a Producer he has been working hard to develop a unique sound that combines hypnotic melodies with profound deep bass lines, organic percussions and minimalistic drums. He has released music on labels like Natural Rythym, Piston Recordings, Chronovision Ibiza, The Purr, InOrbita, and at his own imprint called HAAS Records. His music has been supported by Hernan Cattaneo, Gorge, Detlef, Argenis Brito, Horatio, Paco Osuna, Simone Liberali, Jelly for the babies, Londonground, Manu Desrets & many others.
        </p>
